Acronis is a technology company producing file system - related software tools , including disaster recovery , backup and restore , partitioning , boot management , privacy , data migration , and other storage management products for enterprises , corporations and home users . Its products include Acronis Disk Director Suite and Acronis True Image . Acronis has offices in the United States , Europe and Asia and sells its products through retail outlets , resellers and on the Web . The main product offered by the company is the Acronis True Image line . The company 's primary development facilities are located in Dolgoprudny , Russia . This article does not cite any references or sources . Please help ] improve this article ] by adding citations to reliable sources . Unverifiable material may be challenged and removed . 